# WMS Entegrasyonlar

## Barkod Standartlari (GS1)
```
Barkod Tipleri:
├── EAN-13/UPC-A: Urun tanimlama (GTIN)
├── Code 128: Genel amacli (konum, lot, seri)
├── GS1-128: Lojistik etiketi (SSCC, expiry, lot)
├── GS1 DataMatrix: 2D, kucuk urunler, ilac
├── QR Code: URL, bilgi paylasimi

GS1 Application Identifiers:
├── (01) GTIN: Urun kodu
├── (10) Lot/Batch: Parti numarasi
├── (17) Expiry Date: Son kullanma tarihi (YYMMDD)
├── (21) Serial Number: Seri numarasi
├── (00) SSCC: Palet/koli tanimlayici (18 digit)
├── (37) Quantity: Miktar
```

## Barkod Tarama (ZXing.NET / Camera.MAUI)
```csharp
// Barkod parse
public class BarcodeParser
{
    public ParsedBarcode Parse(string rawBarcode)
    {
        if (rawBarcode.StartsWith("(01)") || rawBarcode.StartsWith("01"))
            return ParseGS1(rawBarcode);
        if (rawBarcode.Length == 13 || rawBarcode.Length == 12)
            return new ParsedBarcode { Type = BarcodeType.GTIN, Value = rawBarcode };
        return new ParsedBarcode { Type = BarcodeType.Generic, Value = rawBarcode };
    }
}
```

## RFID Entegrasyonu
```
Kullanim Alanlari:
├── Palet/koli takibi (UHF RFID, 10m menzil)
├── Asset tracking (forklift, ekipman)
├── Dock door otomatik okuma (portal reader)
├── Bulk receiving (palet bazli toplu okuma)

Protokol:
├── EPC Gen2 (UHF): en yaygin, depo icin ideal
├── NFC (HF): yakin mesafe, mobil cihaz
├── BLE Beacon: konum takibi (RTLS)

Entegrasyon:
├── RFID Reader -> MQTT/REST -> WMS API
├── Tag format: EPC (Electronic Product Code)
├── Batch read: bir okumada 100+ tag
├── Exception: okunamayan tag -> manuel barkod tarama fallback
```

## Label Printing (ZPL — Zebra)
```zpl
^XA
^FO50,50^A0N,40,40^FD{{ProductName}}^FS
^FO50,100^BY3^BCN,100,Y,N,N^FD{{Barcode}}^FS
^FO50,230^A0N,25,25^FDLot: {{LotNumber}}^FS
^FO50,260^A0N,25,25^FDExp: {{ExpiryDate}}^FS
^FO50,290^A0N,25,25^FDQty: {{Quantity}} {{UOM}}^FS
^FO50,330^BY2^BQN,2,5^FDQA,{{QRData}}^FS
^XZ
```
- Label tipi: urun etiketi, konum etiketi, koli etiketi, palet etiketi
- Printer: Zebra ZT/ZD serisi (ZPL), SATO (SBPL), TSC
- Entegrasyon: Raw TCP socket veya print service API

## ERP Entegrasyonu
```
Veri Akislari:
├── ERP -> WMS:
│   ├── Purchase Order (mal kabul emri)
│   ├── Sales Order (sevkiyat emri)
│   ├── Product Master (urun bilgisi)
│   ├── Customer/Supplier Master
│   └── Transfer Order (depolar arasi)
├── WMS -> ERP:
│   ├── Goods Receipt (mal kabul teyidi)
│   ├── Goods Issue (mal cikis teyidi)
│   ├── Stock Adjustment (stok duzeltme)
│   ├── Inventory Snapshot (stok durumu)
│   └── Shipment Confirmation (sevk teyidi)

Entegrasyon Yontemi:
├── REST API (tercih edilen)
├── Message Queue (RabbitMQ — event-driven)
├── Flat file (CSV/XML — legacy ERP icin)
├── Database link (son care — tight coupling)
```

## TMS (Transport Management) Entegrasyonu
```
WMS -> TMS:
├── Shipment request (pickup, delivery address, weight, volume)
├── Carrier preference
├── Service level (express, standard, economy)

TMS -> WMS:
├── Carrier assignment
├── Tracking number
├── ETA (estimated time of arrival)
├── POD (proof of delivery)
```

## Carrier (Kargo) API Ornekleri
```
Turkiye:
├── Aras Kargo: REST API (shipment create, tracking)
├── Yurtici Kargo: REST API
├── MNG Kargo: REST API
├── Surat Kargo: REST API
├── UPS Turkey: UPS Developer Kit
├── DHL: DHL Express API

Entegrasyon Pattern:
├── Carrier Abstraction Layer
│   ├── ICarrierService.CreateShipment()
│   ├── ICarrierService.GetTrackingInfo()
│   ├── ICarrierService.CancelShipment()
│   └── ICarrierService.GetLabel()
├── Her carrier icin concrete implementation
├── Rate comparison: en uygun kargo secimi
```

## IoT Entegrasyonu
```
Sensor Tipleri:
├── Sicaklik/Nem: Soguk zincir izleme (gida, ilac)
├── Hareket: Forklift/AGV takibi
├── Agirlik: Platform tereazi (auto-weighing)
├── Kapı sensor: Dock door acik/kapali
├── Isik bariyeri: Guvenlik alani

Protokol: MQTT (Mosquitto broker)
├── Topic format: warehouse/{warehouseId}/zone/{zoneId}/sensor/{sensorId}
├── Payload: { "type": "temperature", "value": 4.2, "unit": "C", "timestamp": "..." }
├── Alert: threshold asildiginda SignalR ile dashboard bildirimi
├── Storage: time-series DB (TimescaleDB) veya InfluxDB
```

## E-Fatura / E-Irsaliye
```
Turkiye (GIB):
├── E-Fatura: UBL-TR 1.2 format
├── E-Irsaliye: Sevkiyat belgesi
├── Entegrator: Foriba, Logo, QNB, Edepo
├── Format: XML (UBL)
├── Onay: GIB portal uzerinden
```

## Robotics & Automation
```
Otomasyon Seviyeleri:
├── Level 1: Barkod + RF terminal (mevcut)
├── Level 2: Conveyor + sortation system
├── Level 3: AS/RS (Automated Storage/Retrieval)
├── Level 4: AGV/AMR (Autonomous Mobile Robot)
├── Level 5: Goods-to-Person (robotik raf)

WMS Entegrasyon:
├── WCS (Warehouse Control System) layer
├── WMS -> WCS: gorev gonder (pick, putaway, transfer)
├── WCS -> WMS: gorev tamamlandi, hata bildirimi
├── Protokol: REST API veya proprietary (vendor-specific)
```
